			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Open debugbook\r\n2) Got to Region\r\n3) Act 3\r\n4) Wyrm's Crossing\r\n5) Bridge Checkpoint\r\n6.0) oe OIStartOrinJournalist to start the dialog (do the other steps below first if you want them enabled)\r\n6.1) oe OIEnableOrinJournalist to enable journal as Orin\r\n6.2) oe OIMetOrinOnce to enable that you've met Orin in previous impersonation."
				},
