				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "At the end of the queue leading to the South span’s checkpoint is a young journalist taking note and quotes from the poor souls trying to get into Baldur’s Gate.\r\n\r\nLens, a female tiefling in a worn overcoat, can simply be a quiet news worker taking the beat of the outside city (because someone has to tell the true story)."
